title: KSCA Live from the Music Hall Complete [FLAC]
description:
This three volume set was produced for radio station in KSCA FM 101.9 Los Angeles in the mid 90s. The tracks are rare high quality recordings of exclusive acoustic in-studio performances. The radio station itself is long gone. These CDs are out of print.
